## ğŸš€ Getting Started  

### Prerequisites  
- Python 3.8+ / Java 11+  
- PostgreSQL or MySQL installed  
- Git  

### Installation  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/kraryal/Database-Systems-Concepts---Design.git
cd Database-Systems-Concepts---Design
pip install -r requirements.txt   # if using Python
```

### Run Examples  
```bash
python src/normalization_demo.py
python src/indexing_demo.py
```

